text: The Stadionul Municipal is a multi-use stadium in Botoşani, Romania. It is usually used for football matches with FC Botoșani (since 2001). The stadium holds 12,000 people. It was renovated in 2008, 2009 and 2013. == Other websites == *StadiumDB profile Category:Stadiums in Europe
title: Stadionul Municipal (Botoșani)
